1589:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/CMSIS/core/core_cm4.h ****   \details Sets the priority grouping field using the required unlock sequence.
1590:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/CMSIS/core/core_cm4.h ****            The parameter PriorityGroup is assigned to the field SCB->AIRCR [10:8] PRIGROUP field.
1591:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/CMSIS/core/core_cm4.h ****            Only values from 0..7 are used.
1592:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/CMSIS/core/core_cm4.h ****            In case of a conflict between priority grouping and available
1593:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/CMSIS/core/core_cm4.h ****            priority bits (__NVIC_PRIO_BITS), the smallest possible priority group is set.
1594:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/CMSIS/core/core_cm4.h ****   \param [in]      PriorityGroup  Priority grouping field.
1595:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/CMSIS/core/core_cm4.h ****  */
