 333:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/CMSIS/core/cmsis_gcc.h ****   \param [in]    fpscr  Floating Point Status/Control value to set
 334:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/CMSIS/core/cmsis_gcc.h ****  */
