 781:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/stm32f3_hal_lowlevel.c ****   *
 782:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/stm32f3_hal_lowlevel.c ****   * @note   This function uses GPIOx_BSRR and GPIOx_BRR registers to allow atomic read/modify
 783:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/stm32f3_hal_lowlevel.c ****   *         accesses. In this way, there is no risk of an IRQ occurring between
 784:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/stm32f3_hal_lowlevel.c ****   *         the read and the modify access.
 785:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/stm32f3_hal_lowlevel.c ****   *
 786:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/stm32f3_hal_lowlevel.c ****   * @param  GPIOx: where x can be (A..F) to select the GPIO peripheral for STM32F3 family
