 788:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/stm32f3_hal_lowlevel.c ****   *         This parameter can be one of GPIO_PIN_x where x can be (0..15).
 789:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/stm32f3_hal_lowlevel.c ****   * @param  PinState: specifies the value to be written to the selected bit.
 790:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/stm32f3_hal_lowlevel.c ****   *         This parameter can be one of the GPIO_PinState enum values:
 791:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/stm32f3_hal_lowlevel.c ****   *            @arg GPIO_PIN_RESET: to clear the port pin
 792:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/stm32f3_hal_lowlevel.c ****   *            @arg GPIO_PIN_SET: to set the port pin
 793:../../firmware/mcu/hal//stm32f3/stm32f3_hal_lowlevel.c ****   * @retval None
